[[File:Adrenaline_amplifer_belt.jpg|thumb|right|Adrenaline amplifier belt.]]
An '''adrenaline amplifier''' was a type of belt that improved the wearer's reflexes by triggering prolonged bursts of [[Adrenaline/Legends|adrenaline]]. It was thought to be perfectly safe, with only a few instances of uncontrolled muscle spasms.

